30
00:01:25,770 --> 00:01:30,393
For that we need an IEnumerable of select list item.

31
00:01:31,899 --> 00:01:33,840
So let me close this here,

32
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:37,830
and I will add an IEnumberable of select list item.

33
00:01:37,830 --> 00:01:41,460
Call that "RoleList," and for validation,

34
00:01:41,460 --> 00:01:42,897
I will say "ValidateNever."

35
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:47,070
Once we have that IEnnumerable,

36
00:01:47,070 --> 00:01:51,453
we need to populate that inside the "OnGet" right here.

37
00:01:52,410 --> 00:01:55,500
So we need to populate the input is equal to

38
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:57,570
new input model.

39
00:01:57,570 --> 00:01:59,940
We can use the new syntax here.

40
00:01:59,940 --> 00:02:03,150
In there, we want to populate RoleList,

41
00:02:03,150 --> 00:02:06,210
and in order to access all the roles,

42
00:02:06,210 --> 00:02:08,699
typically, we use unit of work,

43
00:02:08,699 --> 00:02:11,280
but when we are working with identity,

44
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:13,140
we have "roleManager."

45
00:02:13,140 --> 00:02:15,120
Inside there we have roles,

46
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:18,450
and that will have list of all the roles.

47
00:02:18,450 --> 00:02:20,220
Now we do not want all the roles.

48
00:02:20,220 --> 00:02:24,540
We will have to project that to be a select list item.

49
00:02:24,540 --> 00:02:27,570
So for projection, we will use "Select,"

50
00:02:27,570 --> 00:02:31,290
and we can say x goes to x.Name.

51
00:02:31,290 --> 00:02:35,130
We only care about the name, we select that name.

52
00:02:35,130 --> 00:02:36,930
And once we select that name,

53
00:02:36,930 --> 00:02:40,920
we will project that into the select list item.

54
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:44,297
So "i" goes to "new SelectListItem,"

55
00:02:46,380 --> 00:02:50,280
and we want to populate "Text is equal to i"

56
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:54,030
and "Value is equal to i," as well.

57
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:56,250
What we are doing is, from roles,

58
00:02:56,250 --> 00:02:58,590
we are selecting only the name.

59
00:02:58,590 --> 00:03:00,900
And whatever we are selecting here,

60
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:03,780
we are adding that to a SelectListItem,

61
00:03:03,780 --> 00:03:07,947
and we are adding that field to both "Text" and "Value."

62
00:03:08,790 --> 00:03:12,120
You can see how projections can get super fancy

63
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:15,360
and how they simplify multiple lines of code

64
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:18,060
in just a few lines of code.

65
00:03:18,060 --> 00:03:22,380
Now the final thing is to display this particular RoleList

