Now again, when you are using asp-for,

76
00:04:06,030 --> 00:04:08,370
it automatically checks the model,

77
00:04:08,370 --> 00:04:11,460
but if you are using any other tag helper,

78
00:04:11,460 --> 00:04:14,133
you have to use the "@Model" before that.

